dadfarnia.ir.MDPF

Class ResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • dadfarnia.ir.MDPF.ResultSet

  • public class ResultSet
extends java.lang.Object
    The result of applying a condition (in the form of PCTL formula) to an MDPF represent in a ResultSet Contains Hashmap of state to valid transitions, as the columnar matrix represent in article.
